cu.explanation_en: Setting local_s_portd to 99999 exceeds the maximum allowed port number, causing F1 interface setup failure and preventing proper CU-DU communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting preambleTransMax to 999 exceeds the maximum allowed value, causing configuration validation failure and preventing proper RACH setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 preambleTransMax 設定為 999 超過最大允許值，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的 RACH 設置。
